{"tid":2085937,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[致所有抗爭者] 午夜過後，勿忘初心","createTime":"2020-06-30T05:59:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-30T06:13:26.000Z","uid":12792,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"2a8c4d0ff9393aae9f81f356b3962a277706e0c8","tid":2085937,"uid":12792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T05:59:53.000Z","msg":"分享網上高質文章<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/e8mFYUw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fe8mFYUw.jpg&h=53ebe4a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n//<br />\n今晚午夜後，結局是怎樣，我相信大部份人都會有一定的畫面，政府會怎樣，坦克又是什麼樣子的，也不想再談。<br />\n<br />\n31年前的天安門，反抗的人不少於香港，甚或倍於香港，逃亡的有多少？繼續抗爭的有多少？餘下的又在哪裏？<br />\n<br />\n逃兵，是免不了的，也不責怪，畢竟恐懼是人性之一，而飼料也是相當有吸引力的。又或者，今天的黃是受了身邊的金影響，黃衣內裡包着的是一顆赤紫心，當真正攬炒時，黃藍陣營才真正歸邊。<br />\n<br />\n如若這是你的信念，請堅守，不要被別人的信念溶掉，有信念的人生才不枉此行。勿忘初心，即使不像你預期。<br />\n<br />\n他，姓胡，名錫進<br />\n當年被稱為&lt;&lt;廣場上的胡錫進&gt;&gt;。<br />\n<br />\n#廣場上的胡錫進 <br />\n#前車之鑒 <br />\n#飼料與自由<br />\n#光復香港時代革命🇭🇰<br />\n//"},{"pid":"5aefdf9b0454e6164e669b7af90cd304ecedccbc","tid":2085937,"uid":235316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T06:07:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">7一維園見</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Facebook ig airdrop</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9vzHhbe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9vzHhbe.jpg&h=c0777e33&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HXtg54z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHXtg54z.jpg&h=eae3d5c9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Qizj3Rf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQizj3Rf.jpg&h=d33e105b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Sg0OXbk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSg0OXbk.jpg&h=791a8ec6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ivfSEpG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FivfSEpG.jpg&h=e07fd1e0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e6dc49ddfda9bea8bda191ba64ea8325742aafaa","tid":2085937,"uid":12792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T06:13:26.000Z","msg":"七一見"}]}